br />\n<br />\n咁千歲鷹貴定snoke 部主艦貴？<br />\n反正同炮都打唔穿個防護網，不如拎部千歲鷹撞佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎千歲鷹撞，入面既人會死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 用千歲鷹撞，可能體積問題，影響力無咁大，戲入面果隻係母艦黎<br />\n2. 自殺式襲擊，人會死，艦會爆，resistance 無乜錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗唔係下下用掛<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下其實都有少少bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光速engine係講緊每部戰機都會有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da30209eff6f32b51e65e87edd91aa994fe6566","tid":502243,"uid":150510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Starwar 入面原來開光速撞人咁大威力<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解仲要裝碌炮上隻艦度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接整d 有光速引擎既無人艦仔撞人未算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用超光速飛行所需要既燃料同引擎貴過整武器囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁千歲鷹貴定snoke 部主艦貴？<br />\n反正同炮都打唔穿個防護網，不如拎部千歲鷹撞佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎千歲鷹撞，入面既人會死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 用千歲鷹撞，可能體積問題，影響力無咁大，戲入面果隻係母艦黎<br />\n2. 自殺式襲擊，人會死，艦會爆，resistance 無乜錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗唔係下下用掛<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下其實都有少少bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光速engine係講緊每部戰機都會有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n光速導彈最好揪<br />\n但死光係現實世界無/未有所以死光型D掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9f035cbcbd9ae7e1c421bc03ca6cffa1ce019f","tid":502243,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"近距離先撞到<br />\n<br />\n啱啱起步未入光速區"},{"pid":"5d8b4ed2676f4ec35ed321bfd8f1aee456f53006","tid":502243,"uid":1802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:5